OL,3,C'Nightmares' of mum whose daughter was
OL,4,Cdismembered by husband
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman who was murdered
OL,7,Fand dismembered by her husband has
OL,8,Fspoken of the "torture" of knowing she
OL,9,Fwas "cast aside like rubbish".
OL,11,FHolly Bramley, who was 26, was stabbed
OL,12,Fto death by her abusive husband, 28-
OL,13,Fyear-old Nicholas Metson, at their
OL,14,Fflat in Lincoln in March last year.
OL,16,FMetson then cut her body into more
OL,17,Fthan 200 pieces and recruited a friend
OL,18,Fto help dump her remains in bags in
OL,19,Fthe River Witham in the village of
OL,20,FBassingham about 10 miles away.
