OL,6,FSome of her body parts have yet to be
OL,7,Ffound.
OL,9,FSpeaking publicly for the first time,
OL,10,FHolly's mother, Annette, said she is
OL,11,Fstill haunted by what happened to her
OL,12,Fdaughter.
OL,14,F"I can't even describe how that
OL,15,Faffected me," she said.
OL,17,F"The nightmares I had, picturing how
OL,18,Fshe must have been so scared in those
OL,19,Fmoments.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
