OL,6,F"Although before we knew everything,
OL,7,F(we knew) that he had done some things
OL,8,Fto her, the full extent was
OL,9,Funbelievable, it was horrific.
OL,11,F"It was torturing to know what he did,
OL,12,Fthat she was cast aside like rubbish.
OL,13,FShe didn't deserve that."
OL,15,FHolly had been with Metson since 2016.
OL,16,FThey married in 2021.
OL,18,FMrs Bramley described her daughter as
OL,19,F"sweet, innocent, loving and caring...
OL,20,Fbut also vulnerable".
