OL,6,FShe said Holly became increasingly
OL,7,Fisolated from the family.
OL,9,F"(Metson) had convinced her that we
OL,10,Fwere all bad people and he was the one
OL,11,Fto save her and that she needed
OL,12,Fsaving. He coerced her into believing
OL,13,Fthat she should cut all ties with the
OL,14,Ffamily."
OL,16,F'He liked to kill animals'
OL,18,FHolly was banned from contacting her
OL,19,Ffamily and friends on social media.
