OL,6,FHer sister Sarah-Jayne Lindop said:
OL,7,F"All she wanted was to find someone
OL,8,Fwho loved her and to have a family.
OL,9,FFamily was everything to her
OL,11,F"He convinced her that he was the only
OL,12,Fone she needed."
OL,14,FMrs Bramley added: "He liked to kill
OL,15,Fanimals and we were fearful for Holly
OL,16,Fbecause of that.
OL,18,F"She was blindsided by love, she just
OL,19,Floved him and believed after time what
OL,20,Fhe was saying must be the truth - that
OL,21,Fwe weren't the right people for her.
