OL,6,F"There were times when he'd send her
OL,7,Fhome (to the family), times when he'd
OL,8,Fbeen violent towards her. My belief is
OL,9,Fthat, had he not sent her home, she
OL,10,Fwould have died a lot sooner.
OL,12,F"That's what he'd imagined himself
OL,13,Fdoing and sent her home to prevent it,
OL,14,Fbut then he would quickly entice her
OL,15,Fback."
OL,17,FBy the start of 2023 Holly had decided
OL,18,Fshe would leave Metson.
OL,20,FShe was last seen on 17 March on CCTV.
