OL,3,C'Nightmares' of mum whose daughter was
OL,4,Cdismembered by husband
OL,6,FIn the following days, Metson put a
OL,7,Fnote on the door of their flat saying
OL,8,Fhe was isolating due to Covid and
OL,9,Fcancelled a takeaway delivery.
OL,11,FAt some point he stabbed her and then
OL,12,Fused several tools to dismember her
OL,13,Fbody.
OL,15,FHe kept the body parts in his flat and
OL,16,Fsent messages to people saying Holly
OL,17,Fhad left him.
