OL,3,C'Nightmares' of mum whose daughter was
OL,4,Cdismembered by husband
OL,6,FHe also made suspicious internet
OL,7,Fsearches, including "how to dispose of
OL,8,Fa dead body" and "can someone haunt me
OL,9,Fafter they die?".
OL,11,FMetson hacked into Holly's social
OL,12,Fmedia accounts to send messages
OL,13,Fimplying that she had left him,
OL,14,Falleging that she had assaulted him
OL,15,Fand transferring money to him by way
OL,16,Fof apology.
OL,18,FPolice were called to the couple's
OL,19,Fflat on 24 March after concerns were
OL,20,Fraised for Holly's safety.
