OL,3,C'Nightmares' of mum whose daughter was
OL,4,Cdismembered by husband
OL,6,FMetson initially denied murder but
OL,7,Fchanged his plea to guilty before a
OL,8,Ftrial.
OL,10,FHe was jailed for life, with a minimum
OL,11,Fof 19 years 316 days.
OL,13,FMrs Bramley is now backing a campaign,
OL,14,Fcalled For Holly, being run by
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police and the
OL,16,FLincolnshire Domestic Abuse Support
OL,17,FService.
OL,19,FIt aims to raise awareness of the
OL,20,Fsigns of domestic abuse and the
OL,21,Fsupport available to victims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
