OL,6,FMrs Bramley said: "I didn't get to
OL,7,Fsave Holly. I want to do something in
OL,8,Fher honour and try and help others in
OL,9,Fthat same situation, make them realise
OL,10,Fwhat outcome they may face if they are
OL,11,Fin that kind of relationship.
OL,13,F"For Holly it was too late and if I
OL,14,Fcan help save just one more young girl
OL,15,Ffrom this same fate then that would be
OL,16,Fjust absolutely fantastic."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
