OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Rachael Cox, a domestic
OL,7,Fabuse specialist at Lincolnshire
OL,8,FPolice, said: "We are indebted to
OL,9,FAnnette. Despite her grief she is
OL,10,Fdetermined to work with us to help us
OL,11,Freach those experiencing domestic
OL,12,Fabuse.
OL,14,F"She is an inspiration and a reminder
OL,15,Fof why we do this job."
